# Generated aggregate specs (voyant#2733). These are multi-megabyte, unviewable
# on GitHub, and rewritten wholesale on any route change — so git does not carry
# them. They're regenerated on demand (`pnpm --filter @voyant-travel/openapi
# generate`) and at `prepack` for the npm tarball. The committed, browsable
# surface is the compact per-module files under spec/{admin,storefront}/.
spec/framework-openapi.json
spec/framework-admin.json
spec/framework-storefront.json
